@{b}   EXAMPLE@{ub}
	...
	char mtxt[20];
	...
	maxlen = date_MonthText(12,&mtxt,English);
	...

@{b}   NOTES@{ub}
	Languages:
	Locale	  : This is an Amiga >= OS2.1 only feature, for <= OS2.0
		    and other systems it will return English text!

@{b}   BUGS@{ub}
	In this version there is no check, if there is enough space in
	wtext!

@{b}   SEE ALSO@{ub}
