@{b}   FUNCTION@{ub}
	Gives you back the time in seconds

@{b}   INPUTS@{ub}
	hour - hours you want (0-23)
	min  - minutes you want (0-59)
	sec  - seconds you want (0-59)

@{b}   RESULT@{ub}
